trans-unit.source: Runs a set of child activities according to a single defined ordering.
trans-unit.target: Executa um conjunto de subordinados atividades, de acordo com uma ordenação definida único.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] The SequenceActivity is a <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.CompositeActivity>, meaning the SequenceActivity can contain other activities.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]O SequenceActivity é um <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.CompositeActivity>, que significa que o SequenceActivity pode conter outras atividades.</xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.CompositeActivity>

trans-unit.source: The SequenceActivity class coordinates the running of a set of child activities in an ordered manner, one at a time.
trans-unit.target: A classe de SequenceActivity coordena a execução de um conjunto de atividades subordinadas de forma ordenada, um de cada vez.

trans-unit.source: The SequenceActivity is completed when the final child activity is finished.
trans-unit.target: O SequenceActivity está concluída quando a atividade subordinada final estiver concluída.

trans-unit.source: Classes that derive from SequenceActivity should not implement the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.IActivityEventListener%601> interface, or the derived class will not execute correctly.
trans-unit.target: As classes que derivem de SequenceActivity não devem implementar o <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.IActivityEventListener%601>interface ou classe derivada não será executado corretamente.</xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.IActivityEventListener%601>
